# A [[young]] [[male]] [[human]]; a male [[child]] or [[young adult]]. {{defdate|from 15th c.}}
#: ''The '''boys''' were playing kickball in the mud.''
#: ''Steve is a '''boy''' of 16.''
# A man of any age, used as a friendly diminutive, or of a man who is merely younger than the speaker. {{defdate|from 17th c.}}
